1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:48,740
=Episode 14=
=Ye Lang Pleads for Love=

11
00:00:52,470 --> 00:00:53,310
Mom.

12
00:00:53,790 --> 00:00:55,110
My wish finally came true.

13
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:56,960
I'm taking Xiaodi

14
00:00:57,110 --> 00:00:58,350
back to your hometown.

15
00:00:59,430 --> 00:01:02,200
This will be the last time
I come to see you.

16
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,760
Sis.

17
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,120
Look!

18
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,040
It's snowing even in summer.

19
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,430
It's really snowing.

20
00:01:26,870 --> 00:01:27,790
He didn't lie.

21
00:01:48,430 --> 00:01:49,310
Niannian.

22
00:01:54,780 --> 00:01:57,540
(One day earlier)

23
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,400
Here, Xiaodi.

24
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,760
Careful, it's hot.

25
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,200
We're leaving Manlong

26
00:02:06,310 --> 00:02:07,760
and going to our mom's hometown.

27
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,130
Over there,

28
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:10,680
they've got better medical facilities.

29
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:12,030
It's a better place to live.

30
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,240
It's safer too.

31
00:02:13,750 --> 00:02:14,610
From now on,

32
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,710
we won't have to live in fear anymore

33
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:18,860
and you won't get lost again.

34
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:22,550
Sis,

35
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:24,800
actually, these past few days,

36
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:27,030
Brother Ye's taken good care of me.

37
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,430
He's only doing it for his own reasons.

38
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,200
Sis.

39
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,160
Not like that.

40
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,120
I can feel it.

41
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,640
He's not bad.

42
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,060
- Xiaodi.
- Who are you?

43
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,840
Don't touch me!

44
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:57,030
My name is Ye Lang.

45
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,800
I'm your sister's...

46
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,240
friend.

47
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,150
My sister's friend?

48
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,080
Why have I never heard of you?

49
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:11,520
What did you do to her?

50
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,680
Xiaodi.

51
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:14,470
This hospital

52
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,310
is the best in all of Manlong.

53
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:18,520
Once you're better,

54
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,560
I'll take you to see her, okay?

55
00:03:20,940 --> 00:03:21,960
Why should I believe you?

56
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:23,560
I want to see my sister now!

57
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:26,960
She asked me to give you this.

58
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,280
You really know my sister?

59
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:31,750
Mm.

60
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,150
Curry's autograph.

61
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:38,680
Once you're better,

62
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,190
I'll take you to play basketball

63
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:42,590
and take you both to an NBA game, okay?

64
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,700
From now on,

65
00:03:46,710 --> 00:03:48,120
if you feel unwell,

66
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,630
go see Dr. Zheng.

67
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,310
He'll contact me.

68
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:57,120
You mean my sister took 200,000

69
00:03:57,470 --> 00:03:58,840
and sold you to a rich woman?

70
00:03:59,030 --> 00:03:59,870
Mm.

71
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,280
Absolutely true.

72
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:02,710
When I tried to leave,

73
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:04,840
that woman came
with eight bodyguards.

74
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,280
She said,

75
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:08,870
"Hey, handsome,

76
00:04:09,430 --> 00:04:11,520
stay with me, and you'll live well."

77
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,040
That does sound like her.

78
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:22,600
She never trusted men,

79
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,830
only herself and money.

80
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:27,310
Back then, she...

81
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:31,470
Anyway,

82
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:33,270
my sister once said

83
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:36,840
if a man would protect her
and make money for her,

84
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,320
then love may happen.

85
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,070
I can protect her,

86
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,480
and I'm rich.

87
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,140
(Brother Ye Lang)
Xiaodi.

88
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,720
I'm going to propose to your sister.

89
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:56,680
- Really?
- Yeah.

90
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,160
Just have your surgery tomorrow.

91
00:05:00,190 --> 00:05:01,240
When you two get married,

92
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,040
I'll bring the rings up myself.

93
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:04,670
Okay.

94
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,510
I'll walk your sister up there,

95
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,270
and place her hand in mine.

96
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,310
When the wedding comes,

97
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,870
I'll buy you the sharpest suit.

98
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:14,870
You'll be my best man.

99
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,840
Okay?

100
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:17,350
Xiaodi.

101
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:22,030
Promise me

102
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:25,630
you'll make it out of the Operating Room.

103
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:29,360
The three of us

104
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:32,750
still have a long future ahead.

105
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:35,910
Mm.

106
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,640
Don't worry.

107
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:40,160
I wanna be an uncle someday.

108
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,880
Okay.

109
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:50,160
Even if he did all that,

110
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,600
it's still true that he lied to me.

111
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:57,030
I just

112
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,560
don't want you to miss

113
00:05:58,630 --> 00:05:59,750
someone good for both of us.

114
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,880
Sis,

115
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,720
can't you give him one more chance?

116
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,680
(When I checked his phone that day,)

117
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,870
(the message that led me here)

118
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:13,310
(didn't seem to be from him.)

119
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,800
(Could someone be stirring this up?)

120
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,000
(Jiang Niannian.)

121
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,840
(You're in trouble.)

122
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:22,870
(You're still making excuses for him.)

123
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,750
Forget it.

124
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,510
Get some rest.
We're leaving the day after tomorrow.

125
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,880
Mm.

126
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,270
How are you feeling?

127
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:40,080
My dear little heart.

128
00:06:42,230 --> 00:06:43,650
You and Jiang Niannian

129
00:06:43,650 --> 00:06:45,540
really are a perfect match.

130
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,120
I honestly thought this time

131
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,070
you'd end up on my autopsy table.

132
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:51,430
What do you mean?

133
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,870
The injury Jiang Niannian caused

134
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,390
didn't hit anything vital.

135
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,040
It was sharp enough

136
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,160
to avoid extra tissue damage.

137
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,750
Your real issue
was excessive blood loss.

138
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:03,720
The blood bank reserves

139
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,720
were used up during Xiaodi's surgery.

140
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,870
That's why you stayed unconscious.

141
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:11,430
In the previous life,

142
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,430
she clearly could have...

143
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:18,150
She clearly...

144
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,400
No.

145
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:26,160
Jiang Niannian didn't intend to hurt me.

146
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,270
Just like previous life,

147
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,660
it was a misunderstanding.

148
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,150
It wasn't her.

149
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,560
It wasn't her.

150
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:38,040
I was such an idiot.

151
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,430
She loved me so much.

152
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:43,270
How could she really do that?

153
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,480
It was me.

154
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:51,800
My own selfish desire.

155
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,630
I thought I could control it all.

156
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:00,880
What do I do?

157
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,600
I feel Jiang Niannian's leaving me.

158
00:08:06,950 --> 00:08:07,790
Bro,

159
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:11,160
I have no interest in dissecting you now.

160
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:12,720
Just focus on recovering.

161
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:33,550
(At this point,)

162
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,600
(why am I still thinking of him?)

163
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:17,730
♪When I come back once again♪

164
00:10:19,890 --> 00:10:24,590
♪I'd still walk toward you♪

165
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:31,740
♪Letting go of all calculations♪

166
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:39,150
♪Just to melt your frozen heart♪

167
00:10:42,190 --> 00:10:44,790
♪When I let go of everything♪

168
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:48,920
I'm sorry.

169
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,440
Forget me.

170
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:59,350
♪Even if the seasons go astray♪

171
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:06,140
♪Cannot forget you
even if the world ends♪

172
00:11:09,590 --> 00:11:13,810
♪I'll take you to see more views♪

173
00:11:14,570 --> 00:11:17,320
♪And leave the mark of my love♪

174
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:20,190
♪The only answer♪

175
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:23,710
♪Is your name♪

176
00:11:23,790 --> 00:11:26,240
♪Don't let me go♪

177
00:11:26,540 --> 00:11:29,360
♪Let me believe it again♪

178
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:38,840
♪Shape unknown roads into your journey♪

179
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,040
Love-brain.

180
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,720
Your precious Jiang Niannian

181
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:58,990
ran away

182
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:00,960
with her brother.

183
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,320
Careful.

184
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,360
He didn't lie to me.

185
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:15,510
It's really snowing.

186
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:25,230
Niannian.

187
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,910
Snow can really happen in June.

188
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,000
Can our love

189
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,320
be reborn?

190
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,200
Sis.

191
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:24,670
Are you really leaving?

192
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,350
Mm.

193
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,150
Actually, that day I...

194
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:34,770
What is it?

195
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:38,750
You always said

196
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:40,080
I was your pride,

197
00:13:41,870 --> 00:13:42,870
but I've always felt

198
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:45,030
I was your burden.

199
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,480
When Mom was leaving,

200
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,120
I promised her

201
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,750
I'd protect you.

202
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,510
But then I got sick.

203
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,000
You had to earn money

204
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,150
to treat me,

205
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,320
and that's why

206
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:05,150
Dad and that woman

207
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:07,790
kept using you.

208
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,280
That day,

209
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,080
I hid some sleeping pills.

210
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:19,120
I wanted to end all of this.

211
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,320
That way,

212
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,960
you wouldn't have to suffer more.

213
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,270
What did you say?

214
00:14:29,020 --> 00:14:30,180
How could you think like that?

215
00:14:31,670 --> 00:14:32,960
Brother Ye found it.

216
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,750
He saw I'd hidden sleeping pills,

217
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,120
but he didn't ask a thing.

218
00:14:44,670 --> 00:14:45,600
He only said

219
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,480
that the one you loved most

220
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:48,920
was me.

221
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,510
That without me,

222
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:54,200
you wouldn't be able to go on.

223
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:57,840
He also said

224
00:14:58,870 --> 00:14:59,750
he would

225
00:15:00,630 --> 00:15:01,600
take my place

226
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,200
to protect you.

227
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:09,590
He promised

228
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:11,750
he'd save you

229
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,550
from those two awful people,

230
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:16,120
and free you from your past.

231
00:15:17,390 --> 00:15:21,150
- (I promise I'd give her a freer future.)
- He promised he'd give you a freer future.

232
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:55,790
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

233
00:15:57,600 --> 00:16:03,810
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

234
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:11,360
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

235
00:16:12,110 --> 00:16:14,580
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

236
00:16:14,580 --> 00:16:19,580
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

237
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:23,810
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

238
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:28,250
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

239
00:16:28,300 --> 00:16:32,090
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

240
00:16:32,090 --> 00:16:37,840
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

241
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:42,160
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

242
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:46,020
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

243
00:16:46,030 --> 00:16:50,520
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

244
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:55,380
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

245
00:16:55,780 --> 00:17:02,320
♪Life finds its way again♪

